  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The table summarizes the distribution of age and assigned group for <math alttext=\"90\"><mn>90</mn>\n</math> participants in a study.</p>\n<figure class=\"table\"><table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<th style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\" scope=\"col\"><math alttext=\"0\"><mn>0</mn>\n</math>\u2013<math alttext=\"9\"><mn>9</mn>\n</math> years</th>\n<th style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\" scope=\"col\"><math alttext=\"10\"><mn>10</mn>\n</math>\u2013<math alttext=\"19\"><mn>19</mn>\n</math> years</th>\n<th style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\" scope=\"col\"><math alttext=\"20 plus\"><mn>20</mn><mo>+</mo></math> years</th>\n<th style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\" scope=\"col\">Total</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: left;\" scope=\"row\">Group A</th>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"5\"><mn>5</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"17\"><mn>17</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"8\"><mn>8</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"30\"><mn>30</mn>\n</math></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: left;\" scope=\"row\">Group B</th>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"6\"><mn>6</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"8\"><mn>8</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"16\"><mn>16</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"30\"><mn>30</mn>\n</math></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: left;\" scope=\"row\">Group C</th>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"19\"><mn>19</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"5\"><mn>5</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"6\"><mn>6</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"30\"><mn>30</mn>\n</math></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\" scope=\"row\">Total</th>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"30\"><mn>30</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"30\"><mn>30</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"30\"><mn>30</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.0583%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"90\"><mn>90</mn>\n</math></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">One of these participants will be selected at random. What is the probability of selecting a participant from group A, given that the participant is at least 10 years of age?</p>",
